2026 2026
1 (viii) District No. 8. The counties of Kearney, Phelps, Hall,
2 Howard, Greeley, Wheeler, Buffalo, Sherman, Valley, and Garfield;
3 (ix) District No. 9. The counties of Lincoln, Keya Paha, Rock,
4 Brown, Loup, Blaine, Custer, Logan, McPherson, Arthur, Grant, Hooker,
5 Thomas, and Cherry;
6 (x) District No. 10. The counties of Furnas, Red Willow, Hitchcock,
7 Dundy, Chase, Hayes, Frontier, Gosper, Dawson, Perkins, and Keith; and
8 (xi) District No. 11. The counties of Deuel, Garden, Sheridan,
9 Cheyenne, Morrill, Box Butte, Dawes, Sioux, Scotts Bluff, Banner, and
10 Kimball.
11 (b) The Governor shall appoint members representing district numbers
12 1, 6, 8, and 11 to serve for terms ending April 1, 2019; members
13 representing district numbers 2, 5, 7, and 10 to serve for terms ending
14 April 1, 2021; and members representing district numbers 3, 4, and 9 to
15 serve for terms ending April 1, 2023. The terms of their successors shall
16 be four years.
